Author: rainbowcatvomit
Text: you are right. the stress and pain will still be there afterwards. and i’ll also have to deal with the relapse, which i don’t want to. so i shall continue to drink my wine and pretend my life is okay. lol good luck to meeeee :D

Author: lmaothrowaway19
Text: friend, just take a breath please stay strong!! just know that b/p is not a good way to cope with your problem- even after you do it, the stress will still be there and will likely be even worse.   you can do this, I believe in you :)
